title: Man-Cave | Watch: Paul O'Connell talks about his last days in the green jersey
text:
No we're not crying, we just have something in our eye.
Paul O'Connell's international retirement was forced upon him this week following the hamstring injury he suffered last weekend against France.
So obviously we got a little bit emotional when Three released the third an final installment of their #AllItTakes series. If you haven't seen the first two, you can do here , but this one has the big man talking about his last days in an Irish shirt before the tournament began. It's all just a bit too much for us, we need a minute.
Thanks for everything Paulie, you've been a monster.
